latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Your heart is meant to be full of love and your belly is supposed to ache from laughter. Your eyes are meant to crinkle on the edges from smiling so much and your soul is meant to feel joy with each new day you are gifted. This is the beauty of life that You are meant to feel peace when you rise each morning and again when you lie your head down to rest each night. This is what your natural state is. This is what beauty of light feels like... peace, excitement, love, joy, laughter, happiness, gratitude. There is not a single person who sees the world how you do. You are a beautifully woven and intricately designed masterpiece. This is what you are made of and this is what you are made for. 
Rejoice each day, rejoice each moment, rejoice the beauty of life.
